{bold}Ambient - Powerful MorphOS Desktop{nobold}
{pp}
MUI based{p}
Fully asynchronous, multi-threaded design, you are never blocked{p}
Does not require icon.library{p}
Built-in original icons support{p}
Built-in newicon support{p}
Built-in OS 3.5 Glowicon support{p}
New true-colour PNG 32bits icon format, with alpha channel support for transparency{p}
Fast icon caching system{p}
File notification{p}
True-colour rendering (no pen allocations){p}
Support for deficons{p}
64-bit arithmetic to handle big storage devices{p}
Localized{p}
ARexx port (optional){p}
Built-in disk formatting{p}
Visual effects: transparency, blurring, colour imposing, alpha channels{p}.
Built-in wbstart.library
{pp}
{bold}New Preferences System{nobold}
{pp}
Highly flexible shared class system{p}.
Possible to embed in MUI applications.{p}
All system preferences can be edited in a single MUI tool{p}.
Or run as a standalone component.
{pp}
